Cryptoweb Domains! You have complete authority over your domains and you dont have to pay renewal fees ever! Cryptoweb domains are Web3 domains (aka NFTs), which you can mint on blockchain and connect to your crypto wallet to make transactions (e.g. send and receive cryptocurrencies), to build website, to use as web3 email through Mailchain!
